structure.unit: Crimes, Punishments And Proceedingsin Criminal Cases

law.catch_line: Warrant For Execution Of Death Sentence; Return To Clerk Of Court After Execution
law.text: When the superintendent has executed the sentence of death upon a prisoner in obedience to a warrant from the court, he shall forthwith make return thereof under his hand, with the doings thereon, to the office of the clerk of said court.
